<h1>Confirm your new email address</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.full_name.presence || @user.email %>,</p>

<p>You requested to change your email address. Please confirm your new email by clicking the link below.</p>

<p><a href="<%= @confirm_url %>">Confirm new email address</a></p>

<p>This link expires in 24 hours. If you didn't request this change, you can ignore this email.</p>
